This folder holds local secret files that are NOT committed to git
(see .gitignore). Create the following files here before running `make`:

  db_password.txt        -> password for the WordPress MySQL user
  db_root_password.txt   -> password for the MySQL root user
  credentials.txt        -> line 1: WordPress admin password
                             line 2: WordPress second user's password

Example:
  echo "Sup3rSecretDBpass!"   > secrets/db_password.txt
  echo "Sup3rSecretRootPass!" > secrets/db_root_password.txt
  printf "AdminPass123!\nEditorPass123!\n" > secrets/credentials.txt
